body:
Successfully built and passes all tests with Clang 10.0.1 on macOS 10.14.5.

I tried building with PROJ.6 and everything built just fine and all of the tests passed. However, according to https://code.mpimet.mpg.de/boards/1/topics/7600, PROJ.6 is still not supported in CDO. I'm going to err on the side of caution and restrict the dependency to `proj@:5`.

@skosukhin
